            <p>Jewellery manufacturing requires much skill and time to get it right. 
            Its an art form that needs the combination of technique and concentration to stroke the metal in a precise way to give it the finish needed.
             Intricate designs could sometimes take months to even years to perfect,
              which is why designer jewellery incorporating heavy designs with foliage and minute details come at a price.</p>
